headline: Nvidia Invests $2 Billion in Synopsys to Broaden AI Design Partnership
summary: The stake expands a multi-year collaboration to develop advanced chip-design and simulation tools.

headline: 2 Large-Cap Stocks with Exciting Potential and 1 Facing Challenges
summary: Large-cap stocks usually command their industries because they have the scale to drive market trends. The flip side though is that their sheer size can limit growth as expanding further becomes an increasingly challenging task.
